{"tid":293014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在南韓外國人破200萬 中國人佔一半最多","createTime":"2017-06-21T22:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T00:03:56.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d410abf7bd8d29098413fadf7664627344faa56","tid":293014,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:53:04.000Z","msg":"在韓外國人破200萬 中國人佔一半最多<br />\n<br />\n2017-06-22 00:16<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓法務部在21日公布數據，顯示去年在南韓境內居住的外國人有204萬餘人，此人數是10年前（91萬人，總人口1.9%）的1倍多，其中中國人最多，有101萬餘人，佔了一半左右。<br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》報導，資料顯示，去年在南韓居住的外國人達204萬9441人，是南韓總人口的4%，最大宗是中國人（101萬6607人），佔了一半，之後依序為越南人（14萬9384人，7.3%）和美國人（14萬222人，6.8%）。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，越南人的人數和過去相比增加不少，2005年的調查中，在南韓的越南人只有3萬8902人，人數落後給中國、美國、日本排第4名，到了2006年增加成5萬4698人，升至第3名，去年（2016）超過美國，變成第2名。<br />\n<br />\n南韓法務部認為，是因為和南韓人結婚的越南人越來越多，加上有不少越南家庭是舉家搬到南韓來居住，才會出現上述現象。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"03fa32d48d732aea11f19b13adb6ce32ea19714c","tid":293014,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:02:32.000Z","msg":"呢兩個地方啲人差無幾架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc608b3d864f575e2b663fd4640267a3f087b2b5","tid":293014,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:03:53.000Z","msg":"大家也是韓國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624570a0b353892a78aa79cfc439511baaf0880a","tid":293014,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:03:54.000Z","msg":"自古以來朝鮮係支那。。。"},{"pid":"71474aeb4eaf27533d2c4017b422309ef664cbcc","tid":293014,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:06:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自古以來朝鮮係支那。。。</blockquote><br />\n自古以來支那屬於韓國的一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4e4460f2b02d3249ac4a260079a469f724b125","tid":293014,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:06:23.000Z","msg":"大家都係中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa85e401344d8c388003cda14e0a803fcd8ab701","tid":293014,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:06:35.000Z","msg":"孔子都係韓國人"},{"pid":"0996768319fe0c81908a08e8590379e6e502536e","tid":293014,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/fvuUYN06wwc/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FfvuUYN06wwc%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=5681d5c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f70a6958aaa80cfc6d662a2cdbab743e6755d680","tid":293014,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:14:36.000Z","msg":"同香港大學一樣走向國際化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35301a8148a9f0208fd13354f305d505ba0c6d56","tid":293014,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:27:26.000Z","msg":"共享中國人榮耀"},{"pid":"5f26507c8a26db6fb746eee005a97e797d67dd9d","tid":293014,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:52:40.000Z","msg":"大家都係垃圾種"},{"pid":"cfc56c6f7ae4cbf6ecab9877ca694b93d27281c4","tid":293014,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T00:03:56.000Z","msg":"支那加不漏洞拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}